you","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"4315d377f9","type":"paragraph","text":"对于一切不幸被俘的仇敌，    你们的英武确实无可比伦。","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"3087d6f558","type":"paragraph","text":"是听清了受难者无言的心声，  还是辛辣的味觉使它们眩晕，","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"e395da56f3","type":"paragraph","text":"它们激怒了，猛一下四爪齐伸，那颗伤残的心便被扯作两份。","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"643288fda5","type":"paragraph","text":"普洛米修士昏晕了，他好像    忽然向暗黑的深渊下沉，","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"1b7321dec1","type":"paragraph","text":"胸膛里有一团地狱的烙铁，    烧烤着，使他的呼吸因而停顿。","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"81cc70de52","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"f7773e6a58","type":"paragraph","text":"高加索山巅清凉的微风， 亲吻着囚徒焦裂的嘴唇，","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"1fe454bef7","type":"paragraph","text":"花岗岩也在颤动而叹息， 他先把普洛米修士摇醒。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"654c4b64f9","type":"paragraph","text":"山林女神们悄然地飞落， 像朵朵轻盈流丽的彩云，","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"494f807c31","type":"paragraph","text":"用她们柔软湿润的长发， 揩拭受难者胸前的血腥。","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"d270925e31","type":"paragraph","text":"她们的眼眶里满含泪水， 她们的声音像山泉低吟……","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"26d6e33e02","type":"paragraph","text":"醒来，醒来哟！可敬的囚人，生命在呼唤着，你要回应。","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"1a5960cf91","type":"paragraph","text":"鹰隼啄食了你的心肺，   铁链捆束着你的肉身，","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"85a378507f","type":"paragraph","text":"但你的灵魂比风更自由， 你的意志比岩石更坚韧……","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"31c0b19e96","type":"paragraph","text":"忽然间正北方响起雷声， 太阳隐乌云翻惨雾雰雰，","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"089a0999b5","type":"paragraph","text":"女神们惊叫了一声“宙斯”！仓惶地四散隐没了身形。","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"79c5c5ab44","type":"paragraph","text":"来了，轻车简从的宙斯， 两肩上栖息着那对兀鹰，","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"4b88aa1172","type":"paragraph","text":"他在普洛米修士头边降落，俯下身察看囚徒的创痕。","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"34097ea1f2","type":"paragraph","text":"看着那纹丝无损的锁链， 看着那血锈班班的岩层，","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"d131c74d22","type":"paragraph","text":"唇边泛起个满意的微笑， 他嘲弄地问道：“怎么样，嗯？”","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"cf129e96fd","type":"paragraph","text":"……囚徒从容地看了他一眼，目光是那么锋利和坚定。","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"bc57c1246f","type":"paragraph","text":"宙斯不由得后退了一步， 觉得在他面前无处存身。","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"49e0488257","type":"paragraph","text":"尽管他全身被钉在岩上， 能动弹的只有嘴巴眼睛，","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"c92de6c50e","type":"paragraph","text":"尽管他躺在这穷山僻野， 远离开人群，无助而孤零。","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"97ddd7e010","type":"paragraph","text":"但这些都安慰不了宙斯， 对着他只觉得刺促不安，","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"cf72fb02e0","type":"paragraph","text":"——他到底保有着什么力量？ 竟足以威胁神族的生存！","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"d78c7ccf5c","type":"paragraph","text":"“怎么样？”他又重复了一句， 口气已变得亲切而和温，","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"933ebaf579","type":"paragraph","text":"“山顶上是不是嫌冷了一些？   不过这空气倒真叫清新。","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"c8d952463e","type":"paragraph","text":"“可恨是这两头扁毛孽畜，     闻到点血就说啥都不听，","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"9a8b41b4be","type":"paragraph","text":"我早已叫它们适当照顾，       不知道它们有没有遵行。","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"b272683d93","type":"paragraph","text":"有什么要求你不妨提出，       能够办到的我总可答应……”","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"1491153734","type":"paragraph","text":"普洛米修士静静地回答：       “多谢你无微不至的关心。","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"f66f676a1e","type":"paragraph","text":"有什么要求：囚犯—就是囚犯， 锁链和兀鹰都无非本份，","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"b98663bb8f","type":"paragraph","text":"只望你收起些伪善，行么？     那对我真胜似任何酷刑。”","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"592c3ecf32","type":"paragraph","text":"宙斯装作像不曾听清，“啊？——我看你有些情绪低沉，","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"ef5ae8bd97","type":"paragraph","text":"那又何必呢！回头处是岸，不怕有多大罪改正就成。","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"0c9231aa2e","type":"paragraph","text":"“你不想再回到奥林比斯，     在天上享受那财富尊荣？","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"98e1cb0dbc","type":"paragraph","text":"你不想重新进入种族家庭，     和我们同优游欢乐升平？”","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"6c4890fec6","type":"paragraph","text":"“可以答复你，宙斯，我不想， 我厌恶你们的歌舞升平，","index":77,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"d4c6afeb37","type":"paragraph","text":"今天我遭受着囚禁迫害， 但我不认为自己是罪人。”","index":78,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"4d057eca78","type":"paragraph","text":"“好吧，那你总还希望自由，   总也想解除惩罚和监禁，","index":79,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"e6c1a7b0d6","type":"paragraph","text":"难道你不向往像平常时日，     随心意飞天过海追风驾云。”","index":80,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"1a360817d1","type":"paragraph","text":"“长话短说吧，你到底要怎么？是的，我酷爱自由胜似生命，","index":81,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"2e7f1be644","type":"paragraph","text":"可假如要索取某种代价， 我宁肯接受永远的监禁。”","index":82,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"3a794e8029","type":"paragraph","text":"“不过是这样，普洛米修士，我们不愿人间留半点火星，","index":83,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"2eb1039374","type":"paragraph","text":"火只该供天神焚香燔食， 那能够给贱民取暖照明！","index":84,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"0f6d73ac8b","type":"paragraph","text":"“当初是你从天上偷下火种，   现在也由你消灭干净，","index":85,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"f94652f79f","type":"paragraph","text":"为了奥林比斯神族的利益，     你应当负起这严重的责任。","index":86,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"c41b4fb5a4","type":"paragraph","text":"还有，由于你从前种种的能力， （宙斯矜持地咳嗽了一声），","index":87,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"2902d955a8","type":"paragraph","text":"据说你预知神族的毁灭，       知道谁将是暴乱的首领？","index":88,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"c4fdbaf690","type":"paragraph","text":"我们不相信会有这种事情，     要推翻神族——梦也作不成！","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"256894f897","type":"paragraph","text":"我们将统治宇宙旷世囗囗，     永保着至高无上的权能。","index":90,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"14e8e67bc6","type":"paragraph","text":"“但也许真有那样的狂徒，     竟想叫太阳从西边上升——","index":91,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"542d3aedda","type":"paragraph","text":"如果你确有所知，就该真说，   让我们早下手惩治叛臣。","index":92,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"9313eb9e7e","type":"paragraph","text":"“普洛米修士，你怎不想想，   你属于神族，并不是凡人，","index":93,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"c20e65bc43","type":"paragraph","text":"大河干，池塘里也要见底，     树倒了，枝和叶怎能生存！”","index":94,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"199b8789d6","type":"paragraph","text":"“那么你已经感到了不稳，     是吗？宙斯，这可真是新闻”","index":95,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"46bca1d29d","type":"paragraph","text":"普洛米修士微微地一笑，       宙斯居然也显出了困窘。","index":96,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"3cd84b5e4c","type":"paragraph","text":"“闲话且慢说，普洛米修士，   接受不接受，你赶快决定。”","index":97,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"39ca5df51a","type":"paragraph","text":"“我不能”。普洛米修士答道， 平静地直视宙斯的眼睛。","index":98,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"f2dac907db","type":"paragraph","text":"“火本来只应该属于人类，     怎能够把它永藏在天庭？","index":99,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"61ec559a8b","type":"paragraph","text":"那怕是没有我偷下火种，       人们自己也找得到光明。","index":100,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"754ec0a155","type":"paragraph","text":"人有了屋子怎会再钻洞，       鸟进了森林怎会再投笼，","index":101,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"c9179a984a","type":"paragraph","text":"有了火就会有火种留下，       台风刮不灭，洪水淹不尽。","index":102,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"4714e140c2","type":"paragraph","text":"火将要把人类引向解放，       我劝你再不必白白劳神，","index":103,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"01a2236822","type":"paragraph","text":"无论怎么样，无论哪一个，     想消灭人间的火已经不成。","index":104,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"82129aa907","type":"paragraph","text":"神族专横的统治那能持久，     你难道听不见，遍野怨声！","index":105,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"6246ff7c5f","type":"paragraph","text":"贱民的血泪会把众神淹死，     奥林比斯宫殿将化作灰尘！","index":106,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"a68d6c2c6a","type":"paragraph","text":"何必问未来暴动谁是首领，     要伸张正义的都是你敌人，","index":107,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"6ec767c069","type":"paragraph","text":"你自己种瓜得瓜种豆得豆，     说不定杀你的就是你至亲。”","index":108,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"de1885e7d3","type":"paragraph","text":"“住口！停止你恶毒的诅咒！” 宙斯两眼冒火脸色变青，","index":109,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"02bdbda94b","type":"paragraph","text":"他扬起雷电槌劈空一击，       平地上霹雳起山摇地震。","index":110,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"90635b1f6b","type":"paragraph","text":"“警告你！我不会轻易饶恕，   切莫要太信任我的宽宏！”","index":111,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"77b624bc22","type":"paragraph","text":"“谁会把你和宽宏联系一起，   那简直辱没了宙斯的英名。”","index":112,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"afc4bba36a","type":"paragraph","text":"“用不着再跟我说长道短，     一句话，你到底答不答应？”","index":113,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"8eac04ab59","type":"paragraph","text":"“重要的并不是我的意愿，     我无法改变事情的进程。”","index":114,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"b7092b63a6","type":"paragraph","text":"“你就这么肯定我们要失败，   哼，瞧着吧，神族将万世永存！”","index":115,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"bcf87603ed","type":"paragraph","text":"“何必还重复陈旧的神话，     问问你自己可把它当真。”","index":116,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"221207be01","type":"paragraph","text":"“难道我胜不过贱民叛徒？     谁敢造反我就把它荡平！”","index":117,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"e88e476a82","type":"paragraph","text":"“我知道在这方面你最英武，   但走多了夜路准碰上冤魂。”","index":118,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"28e75cbfd9","type":"paragraph","text":"“你只能用诅咒来安慰自己！” “这不是诅咒，而是未来的显影！”","index":119,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"fbac245ee9","type":"paragraph","text":"“未来怎样已经与你无涉，     你还是先想法救救自身。”","index":120,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"7d03c0bb4a","type":"paragraph","text":"“你可以把我磨碎，要是你高兴，但丝毫救不了你们的危运！”","index":121,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"6fca7a68ca","type":"paragraph","text":"“你的头脑是不是花岗岩石？”“不，是真理保守了它的坚贞。”","index":122,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"b2f4db7b6d","type":"paragraph","text":"“这么说你要与我为敌到底？”“被你认作敌人我感到光荣！”","index":123,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"f366c05582","type":"paragraph","text":"“我叫你到地狱里去见鬼！”   宙斯怒火万丈吼了一声，","index":124,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"031cd5e178","type":"paragraph","text":"雷电槌对准普洛米修士打去，   只听得轰隆隆像地裂天崩。","index":125,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"027b0de406","type":"paragraph","text":"半边山峰向深谷里倒下，       满空中飞沙走石伴着雷鸣，","index":126,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"64dd21b646","type":"paragraph","text":"电光像妖蛇在黑云中乱闪，     真好比世界末日地狱现形。","index":127,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"5c0a48c215","type":"paragraph","text":"宙斯挥动着手中的槌子，       狞笑着腾身飞上了层云，","index":128,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"db1be1b4ff","type":"paragraph","text":"“难道说我整治不了你？等着！ 不叫你死，剥皮抽你的筋！”","index":129,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"0d30c4e0f9","type":"paragraph","text":"然而他总还是不大痛快，       甚至不感到复仇的欢欣——","index":130,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"9badb7f583","type":"paragraph","text":"……一种阴冷的、绝望的恐惧， 深深地盘踞在他的心胸……","index":131,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"d15a9e2ce8","type":"subtitle","text":"三","index":132,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"6e75d5325d","type":"paragraph","text":"紫色的黄昏向山后沉落，   灰暗的暮霭一点点加深，","index":133,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"cb7696a340","type":"paragraph","text":"残损的山峰却依然屹立，   夜空衬出它深黑的剪影。","index":134,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"2012f50db7","type":"paragraph","text":"普洛米修士悠悠地醒转，   头颅里一阵阵嗡嗡乱鸣，","index":135,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"18bb6ac936","type":"paragraph","text":"砂石埋没了他半个身子，   血污糊住了他一双眼睛。","index":136,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"4413bd2530","type":"paragraph","text":"头上有温热的液体流下，   鼻孔里扑入浓厚的血腥，","index":137,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"676cbbc017","type":"paragraph","text":"他伸出浮肿而木强的舌头， 舐着自己的血来润湿嘴唇。","index":138,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"15af0770a7","type":"paragraph","text":"他用力睁开粘连的眼皮，   看见了几点稀朗的疏星，","index":139,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"fb6ebe1270","type":"paragraph","text":"下弦月淡淡地抹在天际，   夜风送来了杂树的清芬。","index":140,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"25dee7d866","type":"paragraph","text":"啊，夜你是多么宁静，     大地啊你睡得多么深沉。","index":141,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"a3cd4e546f","type":"paragraph","text":"越过广袤的空间，我看见   五谷的田野，繁花和森林。","index":142,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"c4d31a0115","type":"paragraph","text":"江湖水滟滟似银，大地母亲，你好像披着幅奇丽的绣锦。","index":143,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"cfb224154b","type":"paragraph","text":"从远古到如今，你每时每日滋养哺育着亿万的生灵。","index":144,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"61eebcf36b","type":"paragraph","text":"多少人辛勤地开辟与垦植，       大地，你一天天焕发着青春。","index":145,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"c1eb346c17","type":"paragraph","text":"可是为什么，你年年血泪，       只是给众神贡献出祭品！","index":146,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"e28b8e92af","type":"paragraph","text":"我喝过流在你身上的水，         清澈的水是那么苦涩而酸辛，","index":147,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"4f1e6adbf5","type":"paragraph","text":"你胸中迸发出沉重的叹息，       你憔悴了，还有你的子孙。","index":148,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"848540d2ec","type":"paragraph","text":"什么时候，大地，你才能新生，   才能够摆脱被榨取的命运？","index":149,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"e347ae9142","type":"paragraph","text":"啊，万物和人类永恒的母亲，     我胸中膨胀着对你的爱情。","index":150,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"deef1dca3c","type":"paragraph","text":"我知道，一旦你开始觉醒和翻腾， 巍峨的奥林比斯将冰消雪崩……","index":151,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"563e96f62b","type":"paragraph","text":"远远地，在沉睡的大地上，暗黑中出现了一线光明，","index":152,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"60537ad744","type":"paragraph","text":"“火”！普洛米修士微笑地想着，痛楚、饥渴霎时都忘个干净。","index":153,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"071492dc21","type":"paragraph","text":"那一点化成三点、七点、无数，   像大群飞萤在原野上落定，","index":154,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"34bb6c031e","type":"paragraph","text":"但它们是那么皎红而灼热，       使星月都黯然失去了晶莹。","index":155,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"168e07be6e","type":"paragraph","text":"这么多了……好快！连我都难相信，它们就来自我那粒小小的火星，","index":156,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"2e9d4e4c4d","type":"paragraph","text":"半黍火点燃了千百万亿处，光明，你的生命力有多么旺盛！","index":157,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"8d2edffdf2","type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧吧！囗囗在囚禁中，         我祝愿你——","index":158,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"f9f3b261df","type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧在正直的书生的灯盏里，     让他们凭你诵谈真理的教训，","index":159,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"0011190c38","type":"paragraph","text":"把血写的诗篇一代代留下，       为历史悲剧作无情的见证！","index":160,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"7cc324a0bb","type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧在正义的战士的火炬上，     指引他们英勇地战斗行军，","index":161,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"95ba4fd911","type":"paragraph","text":"把火种遍撒到万方万处，         直到最后一仗都凯旋得胜。","index":162,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"c83d40d0a1","type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧，火啊，燃烧在这           漫漫的长夜，","index":163,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"d27063b832","type":"paragraph","text":"冲破这黑暗的如死的宁静，       向人们预告那灿烂的黎明。","index":164,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"05c40a5399","type":"paragraph","text":"而当真正的黎明终于来到，       人类在自由的晨光中欢腾。","index":165,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"894e8527dd","type":"paragraph","text":"火啊，你要燃烧在每一具炉灶里， 叫寒冷、饥饿永离开人们，","index":166,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"5b0801d8cd","type":"paragraph","text":"让孩子拍起手在炉前跳舞，       老年人围着火笑语殷殷……","index":167,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"50c20e48d8","type":"paragraph","text":"凝望那天野上满地灯火，         臆想着未来光辉的前景，","index":168,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"28e32ef767","type":"paragraph","text":"就像正遨游在浩渺的太空，       他觉得精神昂扬而振奋。","index":169,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"9d7215048f","type":"paragraph","text":"今晚，有多少人在灯下奋笔，     记载人民的苦难和觉醒；","index":170,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"888a6b6023","type":"paragraph","text":"多少人正对灯拔剑起舞，         火光映红了多少颗急跳的心！","index":171,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"18890377f0","type":"paragraph","text":"人啊！我喜欢呼唤你，响亮的     高贵的名字，大地的子孙，","index":172,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"1b43183d49","type":"paragraph","text":"作为一个弟兄，我深情地         呼唤：人啊，我多么爱你们！","index":173,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"921c94b93c","type":"paragraph","text":"你们是渺小的，但是又伟大；     你们是朴拙的，但是又聪明；","index":174,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"cb130ca2c9","type":"paragraph","text":"你们是善良的，但是当生活 已经不能忍受，你们将奋起斗争！","index":175,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"9c9d3c121b","type":"paragraph","text":"起来啊！抛弃那些圣书神语，     砸烂所有的偶像和香灯，","index":176,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"77408884ca","type":"paragraph","text":"把它们踩在脚下，向奥林比斯     索还作一个自由人的命运！","index":177,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"3f861f69fe","type":"paragraph","text":"还能忍受吗？这些黑暗的         可耻的年代，结束它们！","index":178,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"f32463f484","type":"paragraph","text":"不惧怕雅典娜的战甲，           不迷信阿坡罗的威灵。","index":179,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"bf732229ac","type":"paragraph","text":"更不听宙斯的教训或恫吓，       他们一个都不会留存。","index":180,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"868192169b","type":"paragraph","text":"人啊，众神将要毁灭，而你们     大地的主人，却将骄傲地永生。","index":181,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"ef9a2fc276","type":"paragraph","text":"那一天，当奥林比斯在你们 的千丈怒火中崩倒，我身上的","index":182,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"1a5e547a98","type":"paragraph","text":"锁链也将同时消失，像日光下的寒冰，那时候，人啊，我将欢欣地起立。","index":183,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"c7bc6777ae","type":"paragraph","text":"我将以自己受难的创痕，         向你们证明我兄弟的感情；","index":184,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"2c7a64fefd","type":"paragraph","text":"我和你们一起，为着那           奥林比斯的覆灭而凯歌欢庆……","index":185,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"b96b086aed","type":"paragraph","text":"在澎湃如潮的灼热的激情里，     普洛米修士翘望着黎明，","index":186,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"98aadf71c3","type":"paragraph","text":"他彻夜在粗砺的岩石上辗转，     倾听哪儿有第一声鸡鸣。","index":187,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"ccc722ff46","type":"paragraph","text":"这些黎明仍会有兀鹰飞来，       但他将含笑忍受一切非刑，","index":188,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"e7c9e9312d","type":"paragraph","text":"因为，随着每一个血腥的日子，   那个真正的黎明正刻刻迫近……","index":189,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"},{"id":"e89f27bccb","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：谭蝉雪编著《求索（兰州大学“右派反革命集团案”纪实）》，2010年。","index":190,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221"}],"page":{"id":"1460d2dc23","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8c96f50221","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}